(31, '<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img data-src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/MOwlO0INfQrBPt2xvkJ7NmkHYrWeDjQKJ2lmvBpXS9RaiaF102N46deavsia3c500U2WqQ0sgqVOEpk6J8GOpMIw/0?wx_fmt=gif&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1" data-w="" data-ratio="0.13043478260869565" data-type="gif" _width="auto" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/MOwlO0INfQrBPt2xvkJ7NmkHYrWeDjQKJ2lmvBpXS9RaiaF102N46deavsia3c500U2WqQ0sgqVOEpk6J8GOpMIw/0?wx_fmt=gif&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1&amp;tp=webp" style="padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.5em; height: auto !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;"></p><section class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI" style="margin-top: 0.5em; padding: 0px 0.5em 0.5em 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; border: 0px; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI" style="padding: 10px; max-width: 100%; border: 2px dotted white; box-shadow: rgb(225, 225, 225) 8px 8px 3px; font-size: 1em; line-height: 1.4; font-family: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(142, 201, 101);"><section class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI" style="padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;">移动设备的用户越来越多，所以我们面向移动终端的WebAPP也开始跟进了。本文主要介绍<span style="padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 22.4px; word-wrap: break-word !important;">WebAPP</span>的开发与调试的相关知识和经验，以及给出几种可选的解决方案。</section></section></section><section class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI" style="margin: 1em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, ''Hiragino Sans GB'', ''Microsoft YaHei'', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; border: 0px; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI" style="padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 1em; font-family: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-color: rgb(142, 201, 101); word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI" style="padding: 3px 8px; max-width: 100%; display: inline-block; line-height: 1.4; border-top-left-radius: 8px; border-top-right-radius: 8px; font-family: inherit; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(142, 201, 101);"><section class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI" style="padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;">一、基本概念</strong></section></section><section class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI" style="margin-top: -1px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; border: 1px solid rgb(142, 201, 101); border-bottom-left-radius: 8px; border-bottom-right-radius: 8px; font-size: 1em; font-family: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI" style="padding: 16px; max-width: 100%; border-bottom-left-radius: 8px; border-bottom-right-radius: 8px; line-height: 1.4; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI" style="padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;">（1） CSS pixels与device pixels</strong></section><section class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI" style="padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></section><section class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI" style="padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;">CSS pixels： 浏览器使用的抽象单位， 主要用来在网页上绘制内容。</section><section class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI" style="padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI" style="padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></section><section class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI" style="padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;">device pixels： 显示屏幕的的最小物理单位，每个dp包含自己的颜色、亮度。</section><section class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI" style="padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI" style="padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></section><section class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI" style="padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;">等值的 CSS pixels在手机屏幕上占多大的位置，这不是固定的，这取决于很多属性。经过分析和总结，我们可以得出这么一条公式： 1 CSS pixels = （devicePixelRatio）^2 device pixels （^2是平方的意思，至于 devicePixelRatio是什么东西，后面会讲解） 。<span class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI" style="padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.4; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1em; text-decoration: inherit; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></section><section class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI" style="padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI" style="padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></section><section class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI" style="padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;">（2） PPI/DPI</strong></section><section class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI" style="padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></section><section class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI" style="padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;">PPI，有时也叫DPI，所表示的是每英寸所拥有的像素（pixel）数目，数值越高，即代表显示屏能够以越高的密度显示图像。（注：这里的像素，指的是device pixe