 word-wrap: break-word !important;">PC上开启fiddler，并在设置中勾选“allow remote computers to connect”</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img data-s="300,640" data-type="png" data-src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/vqlbVFl5Jn32kGVr7JGicHBM1bIULibWRpbZ2W6mBhrTtJZPc9WktUk7cNn0qBhPBRMNLTmASHI2mKV8C4G17o1A/0?wx_fmt=png" data-ratio="0.6602870813397129" data-w="418" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/vqlbVFl5Jn32kGVr7JGicHBM1bIULibWRpbZ2W6mBhrTtJZPc9WktUk7cNn0qBhPBRMNLTmASHI2mKV8C4G17o1A/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;tp=webp&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1" style="padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;"><br style="padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p></li><li style="padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; word-wrap: break-word !important;">手机上设置代理，代理IP为PC的IP地址，端口为8888（这是fiddler的默认端口）。通常手机上可以直接设置代理，如果没有，可以去下载一个叫ProxyDroid的APP来实现代理的设置。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p></li><li style="padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; word-wrap: break-word !important;">此时你会发现，用手机上网，走的其实是PC上的fiddler，所有的请求包都会在fiddler中列出来，配合willow使用，即可实现配host，甚至是反向代理的操作。</p></li></ol></section></section></section></section>', '移动终端开发必备知识');
