ground-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">&nbsp;</p><p style="color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', 微软雅黑, Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 24px; border: 0px; border-image-source: initial; border-image-slice: initial; border-image-width: initial; border-image-outset: initial; border-image-repeat: initial; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-color: transparent; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">2.用Marker添加标注点</p><p style="color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', 微软雅黑, Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 24px; border: 0px; border-image-source: initial; border-image-slice: initial; border-image-width: initial; border-image-outset: initial; border-image-repeat: initial; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-color: transparent; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">&nbsp;</p><p style="color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', 微软雅黑, Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 24px; border: 0px; border-image-source: initial; border-image-slice: initial; border-image-width: initial; border-image-outset: initial; border-image-repeat: initial; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-color: transparent; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">3.关键一步，通过结合定时器，使用Marker创建的标注点实例的setPosition改变标注点位置，实现播放功能</p><p style="color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', 微软雅黑, Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 24px; border: 0px; border-image-source: initial; border-image-slice: initial; border-image-width: initial; border-image-outset: initial; border-image-repeat: initial; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-color: transparent; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><span id="more-2168" style="border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; padding: 0px; background: transparent;"></span></p><p style="color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', 微软雅黑, Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 24px; border: 0px; border-image-source: initial; border-image-slice: initial; border-image-width: initial; border-image-outset: initial; border-image-repeat: initial; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-color: transparent; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">代码分享，直接复制即可使用</p><blockquote style="border: 1px solid rgb(229, 229, 229); border-image-source: initial; border-image-slice: initial; border-image-width: initial; border-image-outset: initial; border-image-repeat: initial; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; padding: 0px 0px 0px 60px; quotes: none; width: 550px; background-image: url(http://blog.xiaoten.com/wp-content/themes/Mossight/images/blockquote.png); background-attachment: scroll; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248); background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: 0px 0px; background-repeat: repeat-y;"><p style="color: rgb(24, 24, 24); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', 微软雅黑, Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 24px; border: 0px; border-image-source: initial; border-image-slice: initial; border-image-width: initial; border-image-outset: initial; border-image-repeat: initial; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; quotes: none; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-color: transparent; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;<br>&lt;html&gt;<br>&lt;head&gt;<br>&lt;meta name=&quot;viewport&quot; content=&quot;initial-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no&quot; /&gt;<br>&lt;meta http-equiv=&quot;Content-Type&quot; content=&quot;text/html; charset=utf-8&quot; /&gt;<br>&lt;title&gt;Track&lt;/title&gt;<br>&lt;style type=&quot;text/css&quot;&gt;<br>html{height:100%}<br>body{height:100%;margin:0px;padding:0px}<br>#controller{width:100%; border-bottom:3px outset; height:30px; filter:alpha(Opacity=100); -moz-opacity:1; opacity:1; z-index:10000; background-color:lightblue;}<br>#container{height:100%}<br>&lt;/style&gt;<br>&lt;script type=&quot;text/javascript&quot; src=&quot;http://api.map.baidu.com/api?v=1.5&amp;ak=D2b4558ebed15e52558c6a766c35ee73&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;<br>&lt;script type=&quot;text/javascript&quot;&gt;<br>//获取所有点的坐标<br>var points = [<br>new BMap.Point(114.00100, 22.550000), new BMap.Point(114.00130, 22.550000),<br>new BMap.Point(114.00160, 22.550000), new BMap.Point(114.00200, 22.550000),<br>new BMap.Point(114.00300, 22.550500), new BMap.Point(114.00400, 22.550000),<br>new BMap.Point(114.00500, 22.550000), new BMap.Point(114.00505, 22.549800),<br>new BMap.Point(114.00510, 22.550000), new BMap.Point(114.00515, 22.550000),<br>new BMap.Point(114.00525, 22.550400), new BMap.Point(114.00537, 22.549500)<br>];</p><p style="color: rgb(24, 24, 24); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', 微软雅黑, Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 24px; border: 0px; border-image-source: initial; border-image-slice: initial; border-image-width: initial; border-image-outset: initial; border-image-repeat: initial; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; quotes: none; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-color: transparent; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">var map; //百度地图对象<br>var car; //汽车图标<br>var label; //信息标签<br>var centerPoint;</p><p style="color: rgb(24, 24, 24); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', 微软雅黑, Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 24px; border: 0px; border-image-source: initial; border-image-slice: initial; border-image-width: initial; border-image-outset: initial; border-image-repeat: initial; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; quotes: none; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-color: transparent; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">var timer; //定时器<br>var index = 0; //记录播放到第几个point</p><p style="color: rgb(24, 24, 24); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', 微软雅黑, Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 24px; border: 0px; border-image-source: initial; border-image-slice: initial; border-image-width: initial; border-image-outset: initial; border-image-repeat: initial; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; quotes: none; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-color: transparent; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">var followChk, playBtn, pauseBtn, resetBtn; //几个控制按钮</p><p style="color: rgb(24, 24, 24); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', 微软雅黑, Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 24px; border: 0px; border-image-source: initial; border-image-slice: initial; border-image-width: initial; border-image-outset: initial; border-image-repeat: initial; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; quotes: none; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-color: transparent; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">function init() {<br>followChk = document.getElementById(&quot;follow&quot;);<br>playBtn = document.getElementById(&quot;play&quot;);<br>pauseBtn = document.getElementById(&quot;pause&quot;);<br>resetBtn = document.getElementById(&quot;reset&quot;);</p><p style="color: rgb(24, 24, 24); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', 微软雅黑, Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 24px; border: 0px; border-image-source: initial; border-image-slice: initial; border-image-width: initial; border-image-outset: initial; border-image-repeat: initial; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; quotes: none; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-color: transparent; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">//初始化地图,选取第一个点为起始点<br>map = new BMap.Map(&quot;container&quot;);<br>map.centerAndZoom(points[0], 15);<br>map.enableScrollWheelZoom();<br>map.addControl(new BMap.NavigationControl());<br>map.addControl(new BMap.ScaleControl());<br>map.addControl(new BMap.OverviewMapControl({isOpen: true}));</p><p style="color: rgb(24, 24, 24); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', 微软雅黑, Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 24px; border: 0px; border-image-source: initial; border-image-slice: initial; border-image-width: initial; border-image-outset: initial; border-image-repeat: initial; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; quotes: none; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-color: transparent; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">//通过DrivingRoute获取一条路线的point<br>var driving = new BMap.DrivingRoute(map);<br>driving.search(new BMap.Point(114.00100, 22.550000), new BMap.Point(113.95100, 22.550000));<br>driving.setSearchCompleteCallback(function() {<br>//得到路线上的所有point<br>points = driving.getResults().getPlan(0).getRoute(0).getPath();<br>//画面移动到起点和终点的中间<br>centerPoint = new BMap.Point((points[0].lng + points[points.length - 1].lng) / 2, (points[0].lat + points[points.length - 1].lat) / 2);<br>map.panTo(centerPoint);<br>//连接所有点<br>map.addOverlay(new BMap.Polyline(points, {strokeColor: &quot;black&quot;, strokeWeight: 5, strokeOpacity: 1}));</p><p style="color: rgb(24, 24, 24); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', 微软雅黑, Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 24px; border: 0px; border-image-source: initial; border-image-slice: initial; border-image-width: initial; border-image-outset: initial; border-image-repeat: initial; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; quotes: none; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-color: transparent; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">//显示小车子<br>label = new BMap.Label(&quot;&quot;, {offset: new BMap.Size(-20, -20)});<br>car = new BMap.Marker(points[0]);<br>car.setLabel(label);<br>map.addOverlay(car);</p><p style="color: rgb(24, 24, 24); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', 微软雅黑, Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 24px; border: 0px; border-image-source: initial; border-image-slice: initial; border-image-width: initial; border-image-outset: initial; border-image-repeat: initial; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; quotes: none; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-color: transparent; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">//点亮操作按钮<br>playBtn.disabled = false;<br>resetBtn.disabled = false;<br>});<br>}</p><p style="color: rgb(24, 24, 24); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', 微软雅黑, Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 24px; border: 0px; border-image-source: initial; border-image-slice: initial; border-image-width: initial; border-image-outset: initial; border-image-repeat: initial; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; quotes: none; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-color: transparent; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">function play() {<br>playBtn.disabled = true;<br>pauseBtn.disabled = false;</p><p style="color: rgb(24, 24, 24); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', 微软雅黑, Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 24px; border: 0px; border-image-source: initial; border-image-slice: initial; border-image-width: initial; border-image-outset: initial; border-image-repeat: initial; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; quotes: none; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-color: transparent; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">var point = points[index];<br>if(index &gt; 0) {<br>map.addOverlay(new BMap.Polyline([points[index - 1], point], {strokeColor: &quot;red&quot;, strokeWeight: 1, strokeOpacity: 1}));<br>}<br>label.setContent(&quot;经度: &quot; + point.lng + &quot;&lt;br&gt;纬度: &quot; + point.lat);<br>car.setPosition(point);<br>index++;<br>if(followChk.checked) {<br>map.panTo(point);<br>}<br>if(index &lt; points.length) {<br>timer = window.setTimeout(&quot;play(&quot; + index + &quot;)&quot;, 200);<br>} else {<br>playBtn.disabled = true;<br>pauseBtn.disabled = true;<br>map.panTo(point);<br>}<br>}</p><p style="color: rgb(24, 24, 24); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', 微软雅黑, Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 24px; border: 0px; border-image-source: initial; border-image-slice: initial; border-image-width: initial; border-image-outset: initial; border-image-repeat: initial; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; quotes: none; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-color: transparent; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">function pause() {<br>playBtn.disabled = false;<br>pauseBtn.disabled = true;</p><p style="color: rgb(24, 24, 24); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', 微软雅黑, Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 24px; border: 0px; border-image-source: initial; border-image-slice: initial; border-image-width: initial; border-image-outset: initial; border-image-repeat: initial; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; quotes: none; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-color: transparent; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">if(timer) {<br>window.clearTimeout(timer);<br>}<br>}</p><p style="color: rgb(24, 24, 24); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', 微软雅黑, Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 24px; border: 0px; border-image-source: initial; border-image-slice: initial; border-image-width: initial; border-image-outset: initial; border-image-repeat: initial; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; quotes: none; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-color: transparent; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">function reset() {<br>followChk.checked = false;<br>playBtn.disabled = false;<br>pauseBtn.disabled = true;</p><p style="color: rgb(24, 24, 24); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', 微软雅黑, Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 24px; border: 0px; border-image-source: initial; border-image-slice: initial; border-image-width: initial; border-image-outset: initial; border-image-repeat: initial; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; quotes: none; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-color: transparent; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">if(timer) {<br>window.clearTimeout(timer);<br>}<br>index = 0;<br>car.setPosition(points[0]);<br>map.panTo(centerPoint);<br>}<br>&lt;/script&gt;<br>&lt;/head&gt;</p><p style="color: rgb(24, 24, 24); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', 微软雅黑, Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 24px; border: 0px; border-image-source: initial; border-image-slice: initial; border-image-width: initial; border-image-outset: initial; border-image-repeat: initial; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; quotes: none; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-color: transparent; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">&lt;body onload=&quot;init();&quot;&gt;<br>&lt;div id=&quot;controller&quot; align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;<br>&lt;input id=&quot;follow&quot; type=&quot;checkbox&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:12px;&quot;&gt;画面跟随&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/input&gt;<br>&lt;input id=&quot;play&quot; type=&quot;button&quot; value=&quot;播放&quot; onclick=&quot;play();&quot; disabled /&gt;<br>&lt;input id=&quot;pause&quot; type=&quot;button&quot; value=&quot;暂停&quot; onclick=&quot;pause();&quot; disabled /&gt;<br>&lt;input id=&quot;reset&quot; type=&quot;button&quot; value=&quot;重置&quot; onclick=&quot;reset()&quot; disabled /&gt;<br>&lt;/div&gt;<br>&lt;div id=&quot;container&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;<br>&lt;/body&gt;<br>&lt;/html&gt;</p><p style="color: rgb(24, 24, 24); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', 微软雅黑, Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 24px; border: 0px; border-image-source: initial; border-image-slice: initial; border-image-width: initial; border-image-outset: initial; border-image-repeat: initial; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; quotes: none; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-color: transparent; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><br></p><p style="color: rgb(24, 24, 24); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', 微软雅黑, Arial; line-height: 24px; border: 0px; border-image-source: initial; border-image-slice: initial; border-image-width: initial; border-image-outset: initial; border-image-repeat: initial; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; quotes: none; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-color: transparent; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><font size="7">原文链接</font></p><p style="border: 0px; border-image-source: initial; border-image-slice: initial; border-image-width: initial; border-image-outset: initial; border-image-repeat: initial; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: