(58, '<p>转载&nbsp;<a href="http://www.daliane.com/npm_err_wu_fa_an_zhuang_ren_he_bao_de_jie_jue_ban_fa/" target="_blank">http://www.daliane.com/npm_err_wu_fa_an_zhuang_ren_he_bao_de_jie_jue_ban_fa/</a>&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: ''Microsoft YaHei'', 微软雅黑, Helvetica, Arial, ''Lucida Grande'', Tahoma, sans-serif; line-height: 22.4px;">npm ERR! Windows_NT 6.1.7601<br>npm ERR! argv &quot;E:\\\\node\\\\\\\\node.exe&quot; &quot;E:\\\\node\\\\node_modules\\\\npm\\\\bin\\\\npm-cli.js&quot; &quot;install&quot;<br>npm ERR! node v0.12.0<br>npm ERR! npm v2.5.1<br>npm ERR! code ECONNRESET</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: ''Microsoft YaHei'', 微软雅黑, Helvetica, Arial, ''Lucida Grande'', Tahoma, sans-serif; line-height: 22.4px;">npm ERR! network tunneling socket could not be established, cause=connect ECONNREFUSED<br>npm ERR! network This is most likely not a problem with npm itself<br>npm ERR! network and is related to network connectivity.<br>npm ERR! network In most cases you are behind a proxy or have bad network settings.<br>npm ERR! network<br>npm ERR! network If you are behind a proxy, please make sure that the<br>npm ERR! network &#39;proxy&#39; config is set properly. See: &#39;npm help config&#39;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: ''Microsoft YaHei'', 微软雅黑, Helvetica, Arial, ''Lucida Grande'', Tahoma, sans-serif; line-height: 22.4px;">npm ERR! Please include the following file with any support request:<br>npm ERR! E:\\study\\angular-phonecat\\npm-debug.log</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: ''Microsoft YaHei'', 微软雅黑, Helvetica, Arial, ''Lucida Grande'', Tahoma, sans-serif; line-height: 22.4px;">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: ''Microsoft YaHei'', 微软雅黑, Helvetica, Arial, ''Lucida Grande'', Tahoma, sans-serif; line-height: 22.4px;">错误代码如上：</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: ''Microsoft YaHei'', 微软雅黑, Helvetica, Arial, ''Lucida Grande'', Tahoma, sans-serif; line-height: 22.4px;">解决办法：</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: ''Microsoft YaHei'', 微软雅黑, Helvetica, Arial, ''Lucida Grande'', Tahoma, sans-serif; line-height: 22.4px;">删除npmrc文件。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: ''Microsoft YaHei'', 微软雅黑, Helvetica, Arial, ''Lucida Grande'', Tahoma, sans-serif; line-height: 22.4px;">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: ''Microsoft YaHei'', 微软雅黑, Helvetica, Arial, ''Lucida Grande'', Tahoma, sans-serif; line-height: 22.4p