(65, '<p style="padding: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 30px; ">作者：廖海洋 QQ:1576701411</p><p style="padding: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 30px; ">首先触发器一但创建好是会保存在数据表中的，它的生命周期会持续到你删除它为止。</p><p style="padding: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 30px; ">下面我来演示下怎样用 phpMmyadmin 创建触发器。</p><p style="padding: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 30px; "><br style="padding: 0px;"></p><p style="padding: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 30px; ">1.新建一个数据库：trigger</p><p style="padding: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 30px; "><img src="http://www.shzlife.com/ueditor/php/upload/image/20160106/1452060851882783.png" title="1452060851882783.png" alt="下载.png" data-bd-imgshare-binded="1" style="padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 730px; z-index: 2;"></p><p style="padding: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 30px; ">2.创建表 test1、test2。</p><p style="padding: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 30px; "><img src="http://www.shzlife.com/ueditor/php/upload/image/20160106/1452060876415459.png" title="1452060876415459.png" alt="下载.png" data-bd-imgshare-binded="1" style="padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 730px; z-index: 2; width: 477px; height: 344px;"></p><p style="padding: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 30px; ">sql:语句：</p><p style="padding: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 30px; "><span style="padding: 0px; "><span class="syntax_alpha syntax_alpha_reservedWord" style="padding: 0px; color: rgb(153, 0, 153); text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: bold; font-family: monospace; font-size: 12px;">CREATE</span><span style="padding: 0px; font-family: monospace; font-size: 12px;">&nbsp;</span><span class="syntax_alpha syntax_alpha_reservedWord" style="padding: 0px; color: rgb(153, 0, 153); text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: bold; font-family: monospace; font-size: 12px;">TABLE</span><span style="padding: 0px; font-family: monospac