(68, '<p>先说一下 android 中 xml 基本语法</p><p><br></p><p>&lt;TextView</p><p><span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">	</span>android:layout_width=&quot;match_parent&quot; &nbsp; &nbsp; 宽度</p><p><span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">	</span>android:layout_height=&quot;60dp&quot; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;高度</p><p><span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">	</span>android:layout_gravity=&quot;bottom|right&quot; &nbsp; 设置浮动（可用或连接符）</p><p><span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">	</span>android:text=&quot;0&quot; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;文本</p><p><span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">	</span>android:textSize =&quot;50sp&quot; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;字体大小</p><p><span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">	</span>android:textColor =&quot;#ffffff&quot; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;字体颜色</p><p><span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">	</span>android:gravity=&quot;right&quot;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">			</span>文字在文本框中的位置</p><p>/&gt;</p><p>这段代码是安卓中文本框的组件，类似html但样式是内联在标签中的。</p><p>常用样式：</p><br><p>layout_height &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;高度 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;match_parent：父元素宽度 &nbsp;wrap_content：拉伸到显示全部内容 &nbsp;dp<br></p><p>layout_width &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 宽度 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;match_parent：父元素宽度 &nbsp;wrap_content：拉伸到显示全部内容 &nbsp;dp<br></p><p>layout_weight &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;权重（比例） &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;设置整数 如：1 2<br></p><p>background &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 背景颜色 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;#ffffff<br></p><p>paddingRight &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 内边距 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;dp<br></p><p>paddingBottom &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;内边距 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;dp<br></p><p>orientation &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;方向 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;vertical：垂直 &nbsp; horizontal：水平<br></p><p>layout_gravity &nbsp; &nbsp; 设置浮动 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;bottom|right<br></p><p>text &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 文本 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Helloword</p><p>textSize &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 文字大小 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;sp</p><p>textColor &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;文字颜色 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;#ffffff</p><p>gravity &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;文字位置 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;left</p><p><br></p><p>常见布局</p><p>&lt;LinearLayout&gt;&lt;/LinearLayout&gt; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;线性布局<br></p><p>* 有一个布局方向，水平或者竖直</p><p>* 在竖直布局下，左对齐、右对齐，水平居中生效</p><p>* 在水平布局下，顶部对齐、底部对齐、竖直居中生效</p><p>* 权重：按比例分配屏幕的剩余宽度或者高度</p>', 'Android入门1-布局'),
(69, '<p>作者：廖海洋</p><p>QQ:1576701411</p><p>获取网络图片并显示这个过程就已经初步涉及到安卓的网络编程了。很多程序都可以通过 HTTP 协议建立连接，获取或发送数据，<br></p><p>安卓也不例外，就像web开发中，前台就可以通过 AJAX 发送/获取后台服务端的数据。</p><p>安卓开发本身就是一个MVC的架构，在安卓上做响应式设计也更加容易。</p><p><br></p><p>前台需要这两个组件，用按钮来触发事件。</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;Button</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; android:layout_width = &quot;wrap_content&quot;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; android:layout_height = &quot;wrap_content&quot;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; android:text = &quot;下载图片&quot;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; android:onClick = &quot;click&quot;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; /&gt;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;ImageView</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; android:id=&quot;@+id/iv&quot;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; android:layout_width=&quot;wrap_content&quot;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; android:layout_height=&quot;wrap_content&quot;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; /&gt;</p><p>后台：</p><p><font color="#008000">//获取图片网址</font><br></p><p>String path = &quot;http://www.shzlife.com/Uploads/thumb_55eaccd0f2697.gif&quot;; &nbsp;<br></p><p><font color="#008000">//获取链接对象</font><br></p><p>URL url = new URL(path);</p><p>HttpURLConnection conn = &nbsp;(HttpURLConnection) url.openConnection();</p><p><font color="#008000">//设置请求方法</font><br></p><p>conn.setRequestMethod(&quot;GET&quot;);<br></p><p><font color="#008000">//发送请求</font></p><p>conn.connect();</p><p><font color="#008000">//获得响应头中的流</font></p><p>InputStream is = &nbsp;conn.getInputStream();</p><p><font color="#008000">//读取出流的对象</font></p><p>Bitmap bm = BitmapFactory.decodeStream(is);</p><p><br></p><blockquote style="display:block; border-left: 5px solid #d0e5f2; padding:0 0 0 10px; margin:0; line-height:1.4; font-size: 100%;">到这里就已经获取到图片流数据了。</blockquote><p><br></p><p>ImageView iv = (ImageView) findViewById(R.id.iv); &nbsp; &nbsp;<font color="#008000">// 寻找显示图片的组件</font></p><p></p><p>iv.setImageBitmap(bm); &nbsp;<span style="color: rgb(0, 128, 0);">//显示图像</span></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><blockquote style="display:block; border-left: 5px solid #d0e5f2; padding:0 0 0 10px; margin:0; line-height:1.4; font-size: 100%;">在这个过程中，需要获取访问网络的权限，且需要在一个子线程中运行，网络工作在主线程中运行是会出现异常的，但是在安卓中想要改变UI,只有在主线程当中运行的程序才可以，显示图片当然算是改变UI了。所以只有将上述的过程放入到子线程中，并且建立一个新<font color="#008000">Handler</font>，</blockquote><blockquote style="display:block; border-left: 5px solid #d0e5f2; padding:0 0 0 10px; margin:0; line-height:1.4; font-size: 100%;">再将子线程中获取到的图片流发送到<font color="#008000">Handler</font>中，配合主线程中显示。在这个过程中，需要用到消息队列机制。</blockquote><p><br></p><p><br></p><p>全部代码：</p><p>public class MainActivity extends ActionBarActivity {</p><p><span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">	</span></p><p><span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">	</span><font color="#008000">//处理消息</font></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="color: rgb(0, 128, 0);">//Handler主要接受子线程发送的数据, 并用此数据配合主线程更新UI.</span><font color="#008000"><br></font></p><p><span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">	</span>Handler header = new Handler(){ &nbsp;</p><p><span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">		</span><font color="#008000">//此方法在主线程调用，可以刷新UI</font></p><p><span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">		</span>public void handleMessage(android.os.Message msg){</p><p><span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">		</span> &nbsp; ImageView iv = (ImageView) findViewById(R.id.iv); &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">		</span> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">	</span> &nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">	</span> &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<font color="#008000">//把位图对象显示</font></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">	</span> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; iv.setImageBitmap((Bitmap)msg.obj);</p><p><span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">		</span>}</p><p><span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">	</span></p><p><span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">	</span>};</p><p><span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">	</span></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; @Override</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; protected void onCreate(Bundle savedInstanceState) {</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; super.onCreate(savedInstanceState);</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; setContentView(R.layout.activity_main);</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; }</p><p><br></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; public void click(View v)</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; {</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; <span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">	</span>Thread t = new Thread() <font color="#008000">//创建子线程</font></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; <span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">	</span>{</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; <span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">		</span></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; <span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">		</span>public void run()</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; <span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">		</span>{</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; <span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">			</span></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; <span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">		</span> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;String path = &quot;http://www.shzlife.com/Uploads/thumb_55eaccd0f2697.gif&quot;; &nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; <span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">		</span> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;try{</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; <span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">		</span> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; URL url = new URL(path);</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; <span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">		</span> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <font color="#008000">//获取链接对象</font></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; <span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">		</span> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; HttpURLConnection conn = &nbsp;(HttpURLConnection) url.openConnection();</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; <span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">		</span> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <font color="#008000">//设置请求方法</font></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; <span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">		</span> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; conn.setRequestMethod(&quot;GET&quot;);</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; <span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">		</span> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <font color="#008000">//设置连接超时</font></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; <span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">		</span> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; conn.setConnectTimeout(5000);</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; <span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">		</span> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; //设置读取超时</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; <span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">		</span> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; conn.setReadTimeout(5000);</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; <span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">		</span> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <font color="#008000">//发送请求</font></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; <span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">		</span> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; conn.connect();</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; <span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">		</span> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <font color="#008000">//响应码为200请求成功</font></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; <span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">		</span> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; if(conn.getResponseCode() == 200)</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; <span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">		</span> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; {</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; <span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">		</span> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">	</span> &nbsp; //获得响应头中的流</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; <span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">		</span> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">	</span> &nbsp; InputStream is = &nbsp;conn.getInputStream();</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; <span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">		</span> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">	</span> &nbsp; //读取出流的对象</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; <span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">		</span> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">	</span> &nbsp; Bitmap bm = BitmapFactory.decodeStream(is);</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; <span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">		</span> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">	</span> &nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p><font color="#008000">// &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">		</span> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">	</span> &nbsp; ImageView iv = (ImageView) findViewById(R.id.iv); &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">		</span> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">	</span> &nbsp;&nbsp;</font></p><p><font color="#008000">&nbsp; &nbsp; <span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">		</span> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">	</span> &nbsp; //把位图对象显示</font></p><p><font color="#008000">// &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">		</span> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">	</span> &nbsp; iv.setImageBitmap(bm);</font></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">		</span> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">	</span> &nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; <span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">		</span> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">	</span> &nbsp; Message msg = new Message();</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; <span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">		</span> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">	</span> &nbsp; <font color="#008000">//发消息到主线程</font></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; <span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">		</span> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">	</span> &nbsp; msg.obj = bm;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;header.sendMessage(msg);</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; <span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">		</span> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; }</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; <span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">		</span> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; <span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">		</span> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; else</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; <span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">		</span> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; {</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; <span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">		</span> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">	</span> &nbsp;<font color="#008000"> //弹窗</font></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; <span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">		</span> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">	</span> &nbsp; Toast.makeText(MainActivity.this, &quot;请求失败&quot;, 0).show();</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; <span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">		</span> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; }</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; <span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">		</span> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; <span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">		</span> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;}</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; <span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">		</span> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;catch (Exception e)</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; <span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">		</span> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;{</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; <span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">		</span> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;e.printStackTrace();<font color="#008000">//抛出异常</font></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; <span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">		</span> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;}</p><p><br></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; <span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">		</span>}</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; <span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">	</span>};</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; <span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">	</span>t.start(); &nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; }</p><p>}</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>', 'Android入门2-获取网络图片并显示');
